                        <interp inst="t18410920-name-577" type="given" value="THOMAS"></interp>THOMAS WEBB</persName>
                  </hi> 
                  <hi rend="italic">re-examined.</hi> This is my watch and flannel shirt-all the other things I have lost.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Cross-examined. Q.</hi> What is the watch worth? <hi rend="italic">A.</hi> Four guineas I gave for it—I had a key of my room, but did not lock it, nor did I lock the box—my watch had a silver chain to it, which is not on it now.</p>
               <p>(Alexander Coleman, Israel Cohen, Samuel Isaacs, Phillip Raphael, Joseph Witney, Lewis Nathan, and Joseph Hart, gave the prisoner a good character.)</p>
